CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 15, 1963, p. 15, reads: "The 1963 Courier-WAMO Home-A-Rama. Pittsburgh's only home and food show, opened before a huge throng last Thursday, June 6, at the spacious Syria Mosque in Oakland...  5. Cott Quality Beverages: George J. Dagenais, general manager, and Thomas Kukle, sales superintendent..."
TitMainTitle: Boy standing in front of George J. Dagenais and Thomas Kukle in Cott soda booth advertising Cott Half & Half - half grapefruit, half lemon soda, at 1963 Pittsburgh Courier - WAMO, Home-A-Rama fair, Syria Mosque
